Ottawa/Canada - It went unnoticed for quite a long time - and finally got noticed. Canadian Green Party leader Elizabeth May has never held the reusable coffee mug with a metal straw in her hand. On the party&#39;s website, she was photographed with this mug, talking to citizens. However, the photo had previously been published and also distributed to the media - and the cup was still a plain (cardboard) cup, as reported by the Canadian National Post.
Green boss has to answer for a photo glitch
