May writes that she feels sorry for the employee who did this. &quot;I don&#39;t want to call him stupid, but there was nothing to hide,&quot; she told the Guardian, while at the same time asking her over-dedicated team: &quot;If they want to edit a picture again, they couldn&#39;t do anything with it make my face look younger?&quot;
